), thee(1x)"},"H608":{"id":"H608","lemma":"אַנְתּוּן","translit":"ʼantûwn","pron":"an-toon'","derivation":"(Aramaic) plural of H607 (אַנְתָּה);","strongs_def":"ye","kjv_def":"ye.","pos":"personal pronoun","usage":"ye(1x)"},"H609":{"id":"H609","lemma":"אָסָא","translit":"ʼÂçâʼ","pron":"aw-saw'","derivation":"of uncertain derivation;","strongs_def":"Asa, the name of a king and of a Levite","kjv_def":"Asa.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Asa(58x)"},"H610":{"id":"H610","lemma":"אָסוּךְ","translit":"ʼâçûwk","pron":"aw-sook'","derivation":"from H5480 (סוּךְ);","strongs_def":"anointed, i.e. an oil-flask","kjv_def":"pot."},"H611":{"id":"H611","lemma":"אָסוֹן","translit":"ʼâçôwn","pron":"aws-sone'","derivation":"of uncertain derivation;","strongs_def":"hurt","kjv_def":"mischief.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"mischief(3x)"},"H612":{"id":"H612","lemma":"אֵסוּר","translit":"ʼêçûwr","pron":"ay-soor'","derivation":"from H631 (אָסַר);","strongs_def":"a bond (especially manacles of a prisoner)","kjv_def":"band, [phrase] prison.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"band(2x), prison(1x)"},"H613":{"id":"H613","lemma":"אֱסוּר","translit":"ʼĕçûwr","pron":"es-oor'","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to H612 (אֵסוּר)","strongs_def":"{a bond (especially manacles of a prisoner)}","kjv_def":"band, imprisonment.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"band(2x), imprisonment(1x)"},"H614":{"id":"H614","lemma":"אָסִיף","translit":"ʼâçîyph","pron":"aw-seef'","derivation":"or אָסִף; from H622 (אָסַף);","strongs_def":"gathered, i.e. (abstractly) a gathering in of crops","kjv_def":"ingathering.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"ingathering(2x)"},"H615":{"id":"H615","lemma":"אָסִיר","translit":"ʼâçîyr","pron":"aw-sere'","derivation":"from H631 (אָסַר);","strongs_def":"bound, i.e. a captive","kjv_def":"(those which are) bound, prisoner.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"prisoner(10x), bound(2x)"},"H616":{"id":"H616","lemma":"אַסִּיר","translit":"ʼaççîyr","pron":"as-sere'","derivation":"for H615 (אָסִ