ב)","strongs_def":"{ambuscade}","kjv_def":"wait."},"H697":{"id":"H697","lemma":"אַרְבֶּה","translit":"ʼarbeh","pron":"ar-beh'","derivation":"from H7235 (רָבָה);","strongs_def":"a locust (from its rapid increase)","kjv_def":"grasshopper, locust.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"locust(20x), grasshopper(4x)"},"H698":{"id":"H698","lemma":"אׇרֳבָה","translit":"ʼorŏbâh","pron":"or-ob-aw'","derivation":"feminine of H696 (אֹרֶב) (only in the plural);","strongs_def":"ambuscades","kjv_def":"spoils.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"spoils(1x)"},"H699":{"id":"H699","lemma":"אֲרֻבָּה","translit":"ʼărubbâh","pron":"ar-oob-baw'","derivation":"feminine participle passive of H693 (אָרַב) (as if for lurking);","strongs_def":"a lattice; (by implication) a window, dovecot (because of the pigeon-holes), chimney (with its apertures for smoke), sluice (with openings for water)","kjv_def":"chimney, window.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"windows(8x), chimney(1x)"}}